,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"치~짱의 얼굴을 봤더니, 어제 「고독한 거리」가 떠올라서……\n왠지, 너무 슬퍼져서……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"슬퍼? 어째서?\n드라마 결말은 해피엔딩이었잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"하지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"후후, 혹시, 드라마 내용을 잊어버렸어?\n그렇지, 함께 마지막 장면 연기해 보지 않을래?\n그러면 기억날 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"어엇!?\n그런 거, 못 해~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"괜찮아, 내가 리드할게.\n틀려도 괜찮으니까, 기억나는 부분까지 해 보자?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"으, 응……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……「어서 거리에서 나가도록 해.\n여기는 더 이상 아무것도 없어.」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"그, 그러니까……\n「자, 잠깐!\n하지만 너는…… 너는 안 가는 거야!?」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"「농담하지 마, 너희와는 살고 싶지 않아.\n어서 내 앞에서 사라져」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"angry01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"………………","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……왜 그래?\n다음은 카오 짱 대사야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"여기서 주인공 일행은 나한테 등을 돌리고\n다신 뒤돌아보지 않고 달려가. 그런 장면이었잖아?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"……하, 하지만……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"odoodo01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"정말로, 너는 그거면 된단 거야……?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"…………!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……카오 짱도 참……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"「그렇다면……\n나와 함께, 있어 줄래?」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"…………!\n「응, 물론!」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-024","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……후훗.\n지금 애드리브, 드라마였으면 NG가 났을 거야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-025","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"뭐엇!?\nNG는 안 된다는 뜻이지……!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-026","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"그러네……\n진짜 녹화할 땐, 안 된다고 했겠지.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-027","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"……후후, 하지만……\n나는, 그런 가능성도 나쁘지 않다고 생각했어.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-028","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":320}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"그러니까 지금은, 우리만의 비밀이야.\n이 이야기를 기억하는 건 우리뿐. 알았지, 카오 짱.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":320,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":320,"voiceId":"event206-01-029","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":321}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"……응!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":321,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":321,"voiceId":"event206-01-030","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(……정말이지, 언제 있었던 일을 떠올리는 걸까.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-031","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(뭔가 해야 할 때일수록 다른 걸 하고 싶어진다는 건\n이런 느낌이겠지.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nnf04","expressionName":"smile03","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-032","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(무심코 방 청소를 시작하거나,\n만화를 읽게 된다는 건 자주 들었지만……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-033","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(……나도 똑같네.\n이런 때에, 오래된 앨범을 보게 되다니.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-034","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(……전부, 이것 때문이야.\n이 티켓……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nnf01","expressionName":"sad01","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-035","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"「졸업 전에, 아기 고양이들에게\n멋진 크리스마스 선물을 주고 싶거든」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event206-01-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":12}],"windowDisplayName":"카오루","body":"「내가 주최하는 크리스마스 공연.\n치사토도 부디 와 주겠니?」","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":12,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":12,"voiceId":"event206-01-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(……너도, 수험생이잖아……\n게다가, 가을에 부활동 은퇴 공연도 했으면서.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(정말로, 카오루답네.)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"결국 마지막까지, 그대로……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-040","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(……지금 와서 무슨 소리야.\n그 시절 카오루는 이제 없어. 그건 이미 받아들였잖아)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-041","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(사람은 모두 변하고, 나아가.\n아야 짱과 파스파레 멤버들도, 그리고 나도)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-042","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(물론, 카오루도 예외는 아니야.\n……카오루의 경우, 좀 과하게 변한 것 같지만)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-043","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(게다가, 지금의 카오루가 싫다는 것도 아니야.\n지금의 카오루니까, 우리의 지금의 관계를 쌓을 수 있었어)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-044","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(그러니까, 아직도 그 시절을 생각하는 게 잘못된 거야.\n더는, 그 시절의 카오루는 없으니까)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-045","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(언제까지나 질질 끌고 있으면 뒤처지게 돼.\n파스파레 멤버들에게도, 카오루에게도, 세계에도)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-046","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(그러니까……)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-047","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"(그러니까 나도, 슬슬 졸업할 때, 겠지)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event206-01-048","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requ